# Deploy

## GitHub
- Repo: https://github.com/hackmods/dickie-lakeshore
- Workflow: `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` — validate + CapRover tarball on `main`
- CapRover needs secrets: `CAPROVER_SERVER`, `CAPROVER_APP_NAME`, plus token or password

## Proxmox (current live LAN host)
- Node: `pve`
- LXC CT **112** — hostname `dickie-lakeshore`
- Site root: `/var/www/dickie-lakeshore`
- URL: http://192.168.0.61/
- Refresh after push: `git -C /var/www/dickie-lakeshore pull --ff-only`
- Stack on CT: Debian 12 + nginx (not Docker)

## Docker / CapRover image
- `captain-definition` → `Dockerfile` (nginx:alpine)
- Copy static assets including `robots.txt`, `sitemap.xml`, `404.html` when those exist
